---
title: Chili-Garlic Beef Noodles with Peppers and Celery
description: Beef and sambal-style sauce make a playful pair in this spicy noodle dish! Savoury vegetarian oyster sauce adds a Southeast Asian twist, while crowd-pleasing crispy shallots add that tasty crunch. These noodles will disappear in no time!
